    <item>
      <title>特斯拉股价像表情包一样飙升，华尔街感到警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/tesla-s-meme-like-stock-surge-leaves-wall-street-feeling-wary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在埃隆·马斯克全力支持唐纳德·特朗普的推动下，特斯拉公司在大选后股价飙升，该公司的市值增加了近 2500 亿美元，这一惊人的数字促使一些华尔街人士敦促投资者保持谨慎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/tesla-s-meme-like-stock-surge-leaves-wall-street-feeling-wary</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 11:21:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>精神航空濒临破产，股东将全部破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/spirit-nearing-bankruptcy-deal-that-would-wipe-out-shareholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与竞争对手 Frontier Group Holdings Inc. 的合并谈判破裂后，精神航空公司即将与债权人达成协议，在破产法庭上重组其沉重的债务负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/spirit-nearing-bankruptcy-deal-that-would-wipe-out-shareholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 01:58:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普乐观情绪推动比特币价格上涨至 90,000 美元以上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/bitcoin-btc-rally-cools-trump-announcement-lifts-dogecoin-doge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币价格在周三早些时候暂停上涨，目前又重新获得动力，推动这种原始加密货币首次突破 90,000 美元，而交易员们正在评估当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对加密货币的言论支持对市场产生的剩余影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/bitcoin-btc-rally-cools-trump-announcement-lifts-dogecoin-doge</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 01:33:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
